name: InterNet Partners
tag_list: internet, ecommerce, seo, content-management, social-media, web-design, search-engine-optimization, web-development
overview:
InterNet Partners helps clients grow their business with branding and marketing strategies via online programs that include web sites, applications and social media.

We provide a variety of services including website design, content management, ecommerce applications, CRM, Data Mining, SEO, SEM, PPC and Social Media Marketing.

We created a methodology called (B2M2), Branding, Building, Marketing, Measuring where we provide clients a roadmap, framework and strategy to follow with all aspects of their online presence.
